des:
New on Netflix Unofficial provides a summary of what TV's and movie shows were added and removed from Netflix in the USA, UK, Canada, and Australia/New Zealand regions.

Select the appropriate feed for your region.

This skill and its data source: https://newonnetflix.info/ are not affiliated with Netflix. This 100% unofficial.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
